WEBVTT

00:01.060 --> 00:01.890
PREVIOUSLY
ON "VERONICA MARS"...

00:01.930 --> 00:03.158
TERRENCE COOK AND...

00:03.200 --> 00:04.121
MISS DUMASS,
THE JOURNALISM TEACHER.

00:04.170 --> 00:06.559
WHO DIED IN THE BUS CRASH.

00:06.600 --> 00:09.307
HE ALSO HAS
SOME GAMBLING ISSUES.

00:09.340 --> 00:11.501
I HAVE INFORMATION ABOUT
THAT MEXICAN KID WHO GOT KILLED.

00:11.540 --> 00:14.976
YOUR 911 CALLER,
AKA TOM GRIFFITH,

00:15.010 --> 00:16.500
IS DR. TOM GRIFFITH.

00:16.550 --> 00:18.279
OUR FAVORITE
PLASTIC SURGEON

00:18.310 --> 00:20.870
SEEMS TO BE OWNED
BY THE FIGHTING FITZPATRICKS.

00:20.920 --> 00:22.512
HEY, DADDY.

00:23.320 --> 00:25.083
SO YOU GUYS
WERE LIKE A COUPLE?

00:25.120 --> 00:27.714
I WAS MADLY IN LOVE
AND 100% GAY.

00:27.760 --> 00:28.909
WHAT IS THAT?

00:28.960 --> 00:30.951
WHAT DO YOU CALL YOURS?

00:30.990 --> 00:33.390
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:38.370 --> 00:40.065
* YEAH, YEAH

00:40.100 --> 00:41.431
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

00:41.470 --> 00:43.165
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

00:43.210 --> 00:45.929
* COME ON, SHAKE IT OUT, YEAH

00:45.970 --> 00:47.471
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

00:47.510 --> 00:49.148
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

00:49.180 --> 00:51.899
* COME ON, SHAKE IT OUT, YEAH

00:51.950 --> 00:53.440
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

00:53.480 --> 00:55.209
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

00:55.250 --> 00:58.219
* COME ON, SHAKE IT OUT, YEAH

00:58.250 --> 01:00.150
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

01:00.190 --> 01:01.452
* SHAKE IT OUT, NOW

01:01.490 --> 01:05.187
* COME ON, SHAKE IT OUT, YEAH

01:12.030 --> 01:14.931
DICK!
YOU TOTALLY NAILED ME.

01:14.970 --> 01:16.506
OH, MAN.

01:16.540 --> 01:18.303
SO YOU'RE THE FINGERNAILS CHICK
FROM MY NEW YEAR'S PARTY.

01:18.340 --> 01:19.637
I DID NAIL YOU.
THAT'S FUNNY.

01:19.680 --> 01:22.035
I REMEMBER YOU TALLER
AND LESS UPPITY.

01:22.080 --> 01:23.707
MY CAR JUST NOW.

01:23.750 --> 01:25.172
OH, JEEZ.

01:25.210 --> 01:26.518
MAYBE WE SHOULD GET
THE HIGHWAY PATROL DOWN HERE

01:26.550 --> 01:28.245
AND TAKE SOME PICTURES
OR SOMETHING.

01:28.280 --> 01:29.645
GIVE ME A BREAK.

01:29.690 --> 01:30.884
I BARELY EVEN TOUCHED
YOUR STUPID DOOR.

01:30.920 --> 01:32.319
YOU LEFI' SOME PAINT.
LOOK.

01:32.360 --> 01:33.987
IT'S ONLY THE MOST VALUABLE
THING ON YOUR CAR.

01:34.020 --> 01:36.227
YOU MIGHT WANT TO FRISK HER
BEFORE YOU GET IN THE BACKSEAT.

01:36.260 --> 01:37.625
SHE COULD BE SMUGGLING JUNK.

01:37.660 --> 01:40.049
YOU'RE ONES TO TALK.
BASEBALL PLAYERS, RIGHT?

01:40.100 --> 01:43.661
REMIND ME. WHICH ONE OF YOU
PITCHES AND WHICH ONE CATCHES?

01:43.700 --> 01:46.498
RELAX, DICK, WE'RE NOT SAYING
THAT YOU'RE GAY.

01:46.540 --> 01:49.907
JUST BECAUSE YOU MAKE OUT
WITH A DUDE HERE AND THERE.

01:49.940 --> 01:51.669
[ LAUGHTER ]

01:55.310 --> 01:59.098
STRAWBERRY SODA.
IT'S A FINE CHOICE.

02:05.250 --> 02:07.252
WELL, WHERE WERE WE?

02:07.290 --> 02:09.781
OH, YES, I REMEMBER.

02:12.760 --> 02:16.196
YOU SURE YOU DON'T WANT
TO TAKE THIS SOMEWHERE ELSE

02:16.230 --> 02:19.836
MORE PRIVATE,
LIKE THE TRUNK OF YOUR CAR?

02:19.870 --> 02:22.737
IT'S CALLED A STOLEN MOMENT
'CAUSE WE'RE SNEAKY ABOUT IT.

02:22.770 --> 02:25.659
EVER CONSIDER THAT MAYBE
YOU'RE NOT AS NOTORIOUS

02:25.710 --> 02:27.029
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE?

02:27.080 --> 02:28.604
COME ON.
ADMIT IT.

02:28.640 --> 02:30.505
YOUR DAD WENT OFF ON YOU
FOR GETTING CUDDLY WITH ME

02:30.550 --> 02:31.972
AT THE CARNIVAL, RIGHT?

02:32.010 --> 02:33.841
MY DAD DIDN'T SAY A THING.

02:35.450 --> 02:36.883
HMM.

02:36.920 --> 02:39.855
MAYBE IT'S JUST THAT I REALLY
WANT TO BE ALONE WITH YOU.

02:40.960 --> 02:44.179
SO WHEN DO YOU WANT TO BE ALONE
WITH ME AGAIN?

02:44.230 --> 02:45.424
SATURDAY.

02:45.460 --> 02:47.690
I'M STAYING AT MY DAD'S
THIS WEEKEND.

02:47.730 --> 02:51.222
YOU CAN COME BY
AND WATCH A MOVIE IF YOU WANT.

02:52.640 --> 02:53.732
I WANT.

02:53.770 --> 02:56.659
I GOT LAMB TURNING
MY HOUSE UPSIDE DOWN.

02:56.710 --> 02:59.634
I GOT THE PAPARAZZI
FOLLOWING ME DAY AND NIGHT

02:59.680 --> 03:01.432
JUST WAITING FOR ME
TO FALL APART

03:01.480 --> 03:03.903
AND MAKE A RUN FOR IT
IN MY BRONCO.

03:04.680 --> 03:07.911
I SWEAR, THERE'S A NEWS CHOPPER
FOLLOWING ME AROUND.

03:07.950 --> 03:10.612
IF LAMB DOESN'T PRESS CHARGES,
IF YOU'RE NOT INDICTED,

03:10.650 --> 03:12.789
THIS MEDIA FRENZY WILL BE GONE
BEFORE YOU KNOW IT.

03:12.820 --> 03:16.153
LET'S CONCERN OURSELVES MORE
WITH KEEPING YOU OUT OF JAIL.

03:16.190 --> 03:17.828
HOW?
I MEAN, YOU SAID IT YOURSELF.

03:17.860 --> 03:20.727
IF ALL IT TOOK WAS A PHONE CALL
TO BLOW UP THAT BUS,

03:20.760 --> 03:22.990
ANYBODY COULD HAVE DONE IT
FROM ANYWHERE.

03:23.030 --> 03:24.395
SO WHY NOT ME?

03:24.430 --> 03:27.263
A GAMBLER, A CHEATER,
A DEADBEAT. WHO'S GONNA --

03:27.300 --> 03:29.097
STOP.
YOU HAD ME AT "GAMBLER."

03:29.140 --> 03:31.608
TERRENCE, RELAX.

03:32.610 --> 03:34.407
JUST TELL ME
WHAT YOU CAN REMEMBER

03:34.440 --> 03:35.702
FROM THE DAY
OF THE CRASH.

03:35.740 --> 03:38.538
I MET THOSE KIDS
OUT AT THE PARK.

03:38.580 --> 03:42.949
AND LIKE I SAID, I TALKED
WITH WOODY, SIGNED SOME STUFF.

03:44.590 --> 03:46.717
I WAS OUT OF THERE
AROUND 5:00, I GUESS.

03:46.760 --> 03:48.557
THE BUS WENT OVER
AT 7:03.

03:48.590 --> 03:50.820
NEXT THING I CAN REMEMBER WAS
AROUND 11:00 MAYBE,

03:50.860 --> 03:53.192
WHEN I TURNED ON THE TV
AND HEARD THE NEWS.

03:53.230 --> 03:56.825
YOU DON'T REMEMBER ANYTHING YOU
DID IN BETWEEN 5:00 AND 11:00?

03:58.170 --> 03:59.762
NOPE.

04:01.370 --> 04:03.201
YOU GOT SOMETHING TO SAY?

04:03.240 --> 04:04.559
YOU REMEMBER NOTHING?

04:04.610 --> 04:07.374
WHERE WERE YOU
AT 7:03 THAT DAY?

04:08.610 --> 04:10.339
I SUPPOSE I DON'T KNOW.

04:10.380 --> 04:12.814
WELL, MAYBE YOU BLEW UP
THE BUS.

04:20.160 --> 04:24.881
"WHO WILL SPOT THE IMPOSTER
CHEERING IN THE SECOND ROW?

04:24.930 --> 04:29.594
HOW LONG CAN MY PEP-SQUAD SMILE
HIDE THE ME I CANNOT SHOW?"

04:29.630 --> 04:31.996
WOW.
THAT IS SO PRECIOUS, MARLENA.

04:32.030 --> 04:37.104
AND YOU EVEN MADE IT RHYME,
JUST LIKE AN INDIGO GIRLS SONG.

04:37.140 --> 04:38.368
I DIDN'T WRITE THAT.

04:38.410 --> 04:39.638
GOT IT.

04:39.680 --> 04:41.375
MUST BE SOME OTHER
PEP-SQUAD LEZ

04:41.410 --> 04:44.277
WHO HAS HER GYM LOCKER
NEXT TO MINE.

04:44.310 --> 04:47.575
OH, WAIT.
HERE'S MY FAVORITE PART.

04:47.620 --> 04:50.214
"TAKING OFF OUR CLOTHES,
I PUT ON MY DISGUISE.

04:50.250 --> 04:56.052
BUT WHEN WE'RE IN THE SHOWER,
CAN MADISON FEEL MY EYES?"

05:02.530 --> 05:04.327
I'VE GOT A PROBLEM.

05:08.800 --> 05:10.836
HAVE YOU HEARD ABOUT
THE PIZZA-BOY MUGGINGS?

05:10.870 --> 05:11.905
I HEARD ABOUT CORNY.

05:11.940 --> 05:13.828
YEAH, CORNY
WAS VICTIM NUMBER FIVE.

05:13.880 --> 05:15.131
I WAS NUMBER FOUR.

05:15.180 --> 05:17.603
LOOK, I NEED YOU TO FIND THE GUY
WHO RIPPED ME OFF.

05:17.650 --> 05:20.847
SOUNDS LIKE
A POLICE MA'I'I'ER TO ME.

05:20.880 --> 05:22.848
I HAD SOMETHING
IN MY WALLET --

05:22.890 --> 05:25.586
A LIST THAT WASN'T
SUPPOSED TO GET OUT EVER.

05:25.620 --> 05:29.784
THAT WHOLE MARLENA THING --
IT WAS MY FAULT.

05:31.160 --> 05:32.320
I DON'T GET IT.

05:32.360 --> 05:34.749
WELL, MARLENA'S NAME
WAS ON A LIST

05:34.800 --> 05:36.665
WITH NINE OTHER
GAY STUDENTS.

05:36.700 --> 05:38.588
THAT POEM EVERYONE
WAS MAKING FUN OF,

05:38.630 --> 05:40.791
MARLENA POSTED IT ONTO A WEBSITE
THAT I SET UP.

05:40.840 --> 05:42.967
YOU SET UP
A POETRY WEBSITE?

05:43.010 --> 05:44.238
A CHAT ROOM.

05:44.270 --> 05:46.773
IT'S CALLED
THE PIRATE'S S.H.I.P. --

05:46.810 --> 05:49.779
YOU KNOW, "STUDENT HOMOSEXUAL
INTERNET POSTING."

05:49.810 --> 05:53.519
I WAS IN CHARGE OF MAINTAINING
USER NAMES AND PASSWORDS.

05:53.550 --> 05:55.177
ONLY THE LIST --
I FOLLOW.

05:55.220 --> 05:59.418
BUT WHY WOULD A MUGGER WANT TO
OUT SWEET LITTLE MARLENA?

05:59.460 --> 06:01.416
BECAUSE SHE DIDN'T HAVE
THE $5,000

06:01.460 --> 06:03.985
HE DEMANDED FROM HER
TO STAY IN.

06:04.830 --> 06:08.425
WHY CAN'T THE EVIL JUST GET JOBS
LIKE THE REST OF US?

06:08.460 --> 06:09.791
WE'RE WILLING TO PAY YOU.

06:09.830 --> 06:11.491
WHO'S "WE,"
AND WHAT ARE YOU OFFERING?

06:11.530 --> 06:14.966
I CAN'T GIVE YOU NAMES,
BUT WE'RE EACH GOOD FOR $100.

06:15.770 --> 06:19.001
FIND OUT WHO'S DOING
THE BLACKMAILING, ALL RIGHT?

06:21.140 --> 06:25.099
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

06:25.150 --> 06:30.816
* BUT I HAVEN'T THOUGHT OF YOU
LATELY AT ALL *

06:31.520 --> 06:33.579
* COME ON, NOW, SUGAR

06:33.620 --> 06:35.781
* BRING IT ON, BRING IT ON,
YEAH *

06:35.820 --> 06:39.620
* JUST REMEMBER ME WHEN

06:39.660 --> 06:44.461
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS
A LONG TIME AGO *

06:44.500 --> 06:46.798
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS

06:46.840 --> 06:50.401
-- Captions by VITAC --
www.vitac.com

06:53.580 --> 06:54.706
SO WHAT THEY'D GET OFF YOU,
CORNY?

06:54.740 --> 06:56.401
OH, ALL THE CASH
AND MY TUNES.

06:56.450 --> 07:00.079
OH, AND THE PIZZA, YOU KNOW?
IT WAS PEPPERONI, THICK CRUST.

07:00.120 --> 07:02.076
IT WAS A REAL NICE PIE.

07:02.120 --> 07:04.782
SOUND LIKE THE GUY
WHO MUGGED YOU?

07:04.820 --> 07:06.287
YEAH, SAME PART
OF TOWN EVEN.

07:06.320 --> 07:08.049
I GOT HIT IN SOUTH NEPTUNE,
DOWN ON ALVARADO.

07:08.090 --> 07:10.888
DO YOU THINK
THEY WERE REAL ORDERS?
NO. BOGUS.

07:10.930 --> 07:12.522
MR. CHO CALLED
BOTH PLACES BACK.

07:12.560 --> 07:14.255
THE PEOPLE THERE
HADN'T ORDERED PIZZAS.

07:14.300 --> 07:17.599
EITHER OF YOU REMEMBER THE NAMES
THAT WENT WITH THE FAKE ORDERS?

07:17.630 --> 07:18.858
YEAH, MAN, I DO.

07:18.900 --> 07:21.460
YOU KNOW AMY ASPARZO
FROM GYM GLASS?

07:21.500 --> 07:24.139
THAT'S WHOSE HOUSE
I WAS HEADED TO.

07:24.170 --> 07:26.309
I REMEMBER DISTINCTLY
'CAUSE I WAS LIKE,

07:26.340 --> 07:30.174
"DAMN, WHAT IF AMY ANSWERS
THE DOOR IN HER UNMENTIONABLES?"

07:31.150 --> 07:32.401
THAT WOULD'VE BEEN SWEET.

07:32.450 --> 07:34.816
CAN YOU GET ME A LIST
OF THE NAMES

07:34.850 --> 07:37.011
AND ADDRESSES THE MUGGER USED,
RYAN?

07:37.590 --> 07:40.184
I'M NOT LETTING HER LEARN
TO SURF ON ONE OF MY BOARDS.

07:40.220 --> 07:42.381
I'D SOONER LET HER PADDLE OUT
ON MY MOTHER.

07:42.420 --> 07:44.081
[ Laughing ]
OF COURSE YOU WOULD.

07:44.130 --> 07:46.553
RIGHT? I'M THINKING
SHE CAN COME WITH US TO CABO.

07:46.600 --> 07:49.228
HEY, YOU TWO LOOK
LIKE YOU'RE IN THE MARKET

07:49.260 --> 07:51.069
FOR SOME SPIRIT PARAPHERNALIA.

07:51.100 --> 07:52.499
I RECOMMEND THE BUTTONS.

07:52.540 --> 07:53.791
THEY'RE AWFUL TEMPTING.

07:53.840 --> 07:55.865
WELL, THEY'RE FOR
A REALLY GOOD CAUSE.

07:55.900 --> 07:57.538
THAT WAS SARCASM,
BY THE WAY.

07:57.570 --> 07:59.674
DUDE, YOU KNOW
WHERE WE GOT TO GO?

07:59.710 --> 08:01.678
WE GOT TO GO
TO SCORPION BAY AGAIN.

08:01.710 --> 08:03.348
THANKS.
CAMPING ON THE BEACH.

08:03.380 --> 08:06.975
ENDLESS RIGHT-POINT BREAK.
THAT'S OUR PLACE, MAN.

08:07.020 --> 08:08.715
[ GRUNTS ]

08:19.360 --> 08:20.793
I NEED YOUR HELP,
VERONICA.

08:20.830 --> 08:23.663
SORRY, KYLEE. I'M WORKING
AT CAPACITY RIGHT NOW.

08:23.700 --> 08:25.497
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

08:27.070 --> 08:28.162
I'M BEING BLACKMAILED.

08:28.200 --> 08:31.806
IT'S JUST...RYAN TOLD ME
I COULD TALK TO YOU.

08:31.840 --> 08:34.206
REALLY?
YOU'RE BEING BLACKMAILED?

08:34.240 --> 08:37.448
SORRY TO BLOW YOUR MIND,
BUT I'M A LESBIAN, VERONICA.

08:37.480 --> 08:38.742
OH.

08:38.780 --> 08:40.941
WELL...THAT'S COOL.

08:40.980 --> 08:42.948
ONLY WHEN YOU'RE
IN COLLEGE.

08:42.990 --> 08:45.288
DID YOU BRING
THE BLACKMAIL NOTE?

08:46.990 --> 08:49.857
I DON'T HAVE THAT KIND OF MONEY.
I'M DEAD.

08:51.130 --> 08:54.099
RESPOND TO THE E-MAIL.
ASK FOR ANOTHER 24 HOURS.

08:54.130 --> 08:56.564
I'LL HANDLE THE CASH
AND DROP-OFF, OKAY?

08:56.600 --> 08:58.522
THANKS, VERONICA.

09:00.240 --> 09:01.935
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

09:01.970 --> 09:04.268
GOT IT.

09:06.410 --> 09:09.174
MARS INVESTIGATIONS.

09:09.210 --> 09:10.905
SURE.

09:14.120 --> 09:16.839
THANKS.
I'LL LET HIM KNOW.

09:20.960 --> 09:22.257
THEY'RE GONNA FAX THROUGH

09:22.290 --> 09:24.827
THAT CREDIT-CARD STATEMENT
YOU ASKED FOR.

09:24.860 --> 09:26.122
GOOD.
THANKS, HONEY.

09:26.160 --> 09:29.129
TERRENCE COOK'S
CREDIT-CARD STATEMENT.

09:29.870 --> 09:35.035
SO...ARE WE WORKING
FOR ACCUSED MASS MURDERERS NOW?

09:35.070 --> 09:36.435
THAT'S RIGHT.

09:36.470 --> 09:37.960
YOU SURE
YOU'RE NOT CLOUDED

09:38.010 --> 09:40.399
BY YOUR YEARS
OF BEING HIS BIGGEST FAN?

09:40.440 --> 09:42.374
I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE.

09:42.410 --> 09:43.741
LET'S JUST CALL IT
A GUT THING.

09:43.780 --> 09:46.442
BESIDES, I THOUGHT
YOU'D BE EXCITED.

09:46.480 --> 09:47.879
BY WHAT?

09:47.920 --> 09:50.286
IF TERRENCE IS GUILTY,
THAT MEANS I'M OFF THE HOOK?

09:50.320 --> 09:53.209
EVERYONE DIDN'T DIE
BECAUSE OF ME?

09:54.790 --> 09:58.624
EXCITED THAT I'M HELPING
YOUR FRIEND'S DAD.

09:58.660 --> 10:01.128
WHERE ARE YOU GE'I'I'ING
YOUR INTEL?

10:01.160 --> 10:02.422
JACKIE AND I

10:02.460 --> 10:06.590
AREN'T EXACTLY THE SISTERHOOD
OF THE TRAVELING PANTS.

10:06.640 --> 10:09.063
SHE'S NOT WHAT YOU'D CALL
HUGGABLE.

10:09.100 --> 10:12.877
WHEREAS YOU WARM RIGHT UP
TO PEOPLE? HMM.

10:13.780 --> 10:15.907
HMM.
HMM.

10:17.210 --> 10:20.748
I WANT TO HELP, AND YOUR GUT
IS GOOD ENOUGH FOR ME.

10:20.780 --> 10:22.372
MM-HMM.

10:22.420 --> 10:24.786
I NEED TO FEEL LIKE
I'M DOING SOMETHING RIGHT NOW.

10:25.920 --> 10:27.615
TERRENCE WILL BE BY
IN A BIT.

10:27.660 --> 10:30.083
WOULD YOU MIND MAKING
A COUPLE CALLS FOR ME?

10:30.130 --> 10:31.825
NO SWEAT.

10:38.970 --> 10:41.131
YOU CAN HEAD RIGHT IN.

10:41.170 --> 10:42.467
HI.

10:42.500 --> 10:45.401
THIS IS VERONICA MARS CALLING
FROM MARS INVESTIGATIONS.

10:45.440 --> 10:48.204
I'VE GOT CALLS MADE
TO YOUR AGENT, YOUR BROTHER,

10:48.240 --> 10:50.800
YOUR ASSISTANT --
ON AND ON.

10:50.850 --> 10:54.115
NO ONE SEEMS TO KNOW WHERE YOU
WERE WHEN YOU MADE THEM.

10:54.150 --> 10:56.015
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

10:56.050 --> 10:58.211
GOT SOMETHING.
MY DAUGHTER.

10:58.250 --> 10:59.182
YEAH, WE'VE MET.

10:59.220 --> 11:01.484
YOU KNOW THE NAME
HANK MELTON?

11:01.520 --> 11:03.283
NO.

11:03.330 --> 11:05.753
HE WORKS FOR MINT CONDITION CAR
DETAILING OFF THE INTERSTATE.

11:05.790 --> 11:08.224
OH, CRAZY HANK?
YEAH, I KNOW THAT GUY.

11:08.260 --> 11:11.696
HE WORKS ON MY CAR
WHENEVER.

11:13.600 --> 11:15.830
VERONICA,
CAN YOU GIVE US A MINUTE?

11:21.740 --> 11:23.276
TERRENCE?

11:23.310 --> 11:25.744
I CALL HANK WHENEVER I HIT
THE SEVEN RIVERS CASINO.

11:25.780 --> 11:27.509
SO YOU WERE IN THE CASINO
THAT DAY,

11:27.550 --> 11:28.949
POSSIBLY
WHEN THE BUS CRASHED?

11:28.980 --> 11:29.947
I SAY IT'S LIKELY.

11:29.990 --> 11:31.548
THAT'S GREAT NEWS.

11:31.590 --> 11:34.354
CASINOS HAPPEN TO BE THE MOST
PHOTOGRAPHED PLACES ON EARTH.

11:34.390 --> 11:37.154
GOOD LUCK GETTING THAT
SURVEILLANCE FOOTAGE, KEITH.

11:37.190 --> 11:39.579
DO YOU KNOW
WHO LEONARD LOBO IS?

11:39.630 --> 11:41.120
THE GUY WHO RUNS
SEVEN RIVERS?

11:41.160 --> 11:43.469
ACTUALLY, SEVERAL
OF THE INDIAN CASINOS.

11:43.500 --> 11:44.967
WHAT'S LOBO GOT
AGAINST YOU?

11:45.000 --> 11:48.163
MILLIONS OF DOLLARS' WORTH
OF OUTSTANDING DEBT.

11:48.200 --> 11:50.862
YOU KNOW THOSE GUYS
THE SHERIFF CAUGHT LOITERING

11:50.910 --> 11:52.263
OUTSIDE OF MY HOUSE?

11:52.310 --> 11:53.379
FITZPATRICKS.

11:53.410 --> 11:55.275
DELIVERING A MESSAGE
FOR LEONARD LOBO.

11:55.310 --> 11:58.074
HIS WAY OF SAYING
THAT MY PAYMENTS ARE OVERDUE.

11:58.880 --> 12:01.769
MR. PLEACHER AND THE NEPTUNE
HIGH SCIENCE DEPARTMENT

12:01.820 --> 12:04.687
WOULD LIKE TO INVITE YOU ALL
TO THE ANNUAL PHYSICS OLYMPICS.

12:04.720 --> 12:07.712
COMPETITION WILL BE HELD...

12:09.060 --> 12:10.527
LAST NIGHT WAS A BUST?

12:10.560 --> 12:13.893
WHAT, TWO HOURS SPENT TRACKING
A DUMMY E-MAIL ADDRESS?

12:13.930 --> 12:15.454
MAYBE THIS WILL HELP.

12:15.500 --> 12:19.288
ALL THE NAMES AND ADDRESSES
TO ANY ORDERED PIZZAS.

12:19.330 --> 12:21.195
YOU GOT TO DO SOMETHING,
VERONICA.

12:21.240 --> 12:23.162
I'M GETTING
LIKE 100 E-MAILS A DAY

12:23.210 --> 12:24.734
FROM MY PIRATE'S S.H.I.P.
PEEPS.

12:24.770 --> 12:26.874
THEY'RE REALLY STARTING
TO FREAK.

12:28.210 --> 12:29.848
WHAT?
YOU KNOW ONE OF THEM?

12:29.880 --> 12:31.802
LET'S GO TO KYLEE MARKER
FOR THE STORY.

12:31.850 --> 12:34.318
SHE'S OUT
IN THE PARKING LOT LIVE.

12:34.350 --> 12:36.568
Kylee: THE PIZZA-BOY MUGGER
ADDED TO HIS REPERTOIRE.

12:36.620 --> 12:39.418
ALTHOUGH THE M.O. WAS THE SAME,
A TASER TO THE NECK,

12:39.450 --> 12:42.055
THIS TIME HE CHOSE A SEEMINGLY
RANDOM VICTIM --

12:42.090 --> 12:44.627
BASEBALL PLAYER KELLY KUZZIO.

12:44.660 --> 12:46.321
Kelly:
AFI'ER LAST NIGHT'S GAME,

12:46.360 --> 12:48.521
I STOPPED AT SAC-N-PAC
TO GRAB A DRINK.

12:48.560 --> 12:52.189
GOT OUT OF MY CAR AND BAM!
LIGHTS OUT.

12:52.230 --> 12:53.936
HE TOOK MY WATCH,
MY WALLET.

12:53.970 --> 12:57.428
BUT WHAT REALLY SUCKED --
HE STOLE MY RIMS.

12:57.470 --> 12:59.199
SIX GRAND THOSE COST ME.

12:59.240 --> 13:03.176
BEFORE I SEND IT BACK, I'D LIKE
TO ADD A PERSONAL MESSAGE.

13:03.210 --> 13:04.347
I'M GAY.

13:04.380 --> 13:06.200
MARLENA NICHOLS
IS MY GIRLFRIEND.

13:06.250 --> 13:07.945
SO, PIZZA-BOY MUGGER,

13:07.980 --> 13:10.483
YOU CAN FORGET
ABOUT COLLECTING FROM ME.

13:10.520 --> 13:12.010
JOHN?

13:13.390 --> 13:16.985
WELL, IT LOOKS LIKE KYLEE WON'T
BE NEEDING MY HELP ANYMORE.

13:32.570 --> 13:36.506
THAT TOTALLY ROCKS.

13:38.550 --> 13:41.872
DUDE, WHY ARE LESBIANS, LIKE,
SO PISSED OFF ALL THE TIME?

13:41.920 --> 13:44.684
LET YOUR FREAK FLAG FLY,
LADIES!

13:44.720 --> 13:46.540
HOW PROGRESSIVE
OF YOU, DICK.

13:46.590 --> 13:48.285
DAMN.
WHAT IS IT WITH YOU?

13:48.320 --> 13:51.153
DO YOU FOLLOW ME AROUND
FOR FUN OR WHAT?

13:51.190 --> 13:52.896
WOULD IT HELP
IF I STARTED MAKING OUT

13:52.930 --> 13:54.898
WITH MY GIRLFRIEND
IN THE HALL?

13:54.930 --> 13:56.295
YEAH, OBVIOUSLY.

13:56.330 --> 13:59.219
BUT, LOOK, I'LL FIX YOUR CAR,
WHATEVER.

13:59.270 --> 14:01.158
YOU GOT TO LEARN
TO LEAVE ME ALONE.

14:01.200 --> 14:04.738
AND HERE I THOUGHT
WE WERE GETTING TO BE PALS.

14:04.770 --> 14:06.067
PLEASE.

14:06.110 --> 14:07.577
YOU DATE LOGAN.
HE'S NAILED FOR MURDER.

14:07.610 --> 14:09.305
YOU DATE DUNCAN.
HE'S WANTED FOR KIDNAPPING.

14:09.340 --> 14:11.171
YOU GET PUT ON ROBBIE
AND HUNTER'S JURY,

14:11.210 --> 14:12.643
THEY GET SENT TO CHINO.

14:12.680 --> 14:15.319
YOU'RE LIKE RICH-DUDE
KRYPTONITE, VERONICA.

14:15.350 --> 14:18.239
THIS RICH DUDE
WANTS NO PART OF IT.

14:24.330 --> 14:26.321
HEY, CARMEN.

14:26.360 --> 14:29.727
HEARD FROM OUR FAVORITE
VIDEOGRAPHER LATELY?

14:29.760 --> 14:31.227
HE CALLED OVER CHRISTMAS

14:31.270 --> 14:33.966
TO TRY TO APOLOGIZE
FOR THAT WHOLE POPSICLE THING.

14:34.000 --> 14:36.867
LIKE PEOPLE EVEN REMEMBER
MY SCAN DAL ANYMORE.

14:36.910 --> 14:39.367
PLEASURING INANIMATE OBJECTS
WAS SO 2005.

14:39.410 --> 14:42.709
YEAH, THIS YEAR'S ALL ABOUT
PULLING KIDS OUT OF THE CLOSET.

14:42.740 --> 14:46.198
SO I HAVE A FEELING WE'RE
NOT JUST CATCHING UP HERE.

14:47.620 --> 14:50.248
ANY IDEA WHY THE PIZZA MUGGER
USED YOUR NAME?

14:50.290 --> 14:51.314
NO.

14:51.350 --> 14:53.079
YOU MIND LOOKING
AT SOMETHING?

14:53.120 --> 14:57.181
OBVIOUSLY YOU, JOHN RAMOS,
AND AMY ARE ALL STUDENTS.

14:57.230 --> 15:00.154
YOU LIVE RELATIVELY CLOSE,
BUT IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE

15:00.200 --> 15:03.169
THAT WOULD TIE YOU TOGETHER
IN THE MUGGER'S MIND?

15:03.200 --> 15:05.259
WE'RE ALL COCONUTS.

15:06.000 --> 15:08.696
THAT'S WHAT YOU GET CALLED
IN NEPTUNE WHEN YOU'RE LATINO

15:10.840 --> 15:12.535
GET IT?
LIKE TWINKIES AND OREOS.

15:12.570 --> 15:14.902
EXCEPT WE'RE BROWN
ON THE OUTSIDE AND --

15:14.940 --> 15:17.408
I GET IT.
I...I'M SORRY.

15:17.450 --> 15:20.146
HEY, YOU DIDN'T MAKE
THE RULES.

15:20.950 --> 15:23.282
I HOPE YOU GET YOUR BAD GUY,
VERONICA.

15:23.320 --> 15:25.117
ACTUALLY, YOU COULD HELP.

15:25.150 --> 15:28.358
CAN YOU MAKE ME A LIST
OF EVERYONE YOU CAN THINK OF

15:28.390 --> 15:31.928
WHO GETS MADE FUN OF
FOR -- YOU KNOW...

15:32.590 --> 15:35.650
...BEING A COCONUT?

15:37.070 --> 15:39.391
SORRY ABOUT YOUR CAR,
KELLY.

15:39.430 --> 15:40.590
YEAH. THAN KS.

15:40.640 --> 15:42.665
DID YOU GET A LOOK
AT THE GUY WHO ZAPPED YOU?

15:42.700 --> 15:44.031
NO. NOTHING.

15:44.070 --> 15:45.833
I WAS GETTING IN MY CAR
AT THE SAC-N-PAC.

15:45.870 --> 15:49.499
NEXT THING I KNEW, I WAS WAKING
UP AND MY CAR WAS UP ON BLOCKS.

15:49.540 --> 15:51.246
YOU MUST HAVE BEEN OUT
A LONG TIME.

15:51.280 --> 15:53.111
I CAN'T BELIEVE
NO ONE CALLED THE COPS.

15:53.150 --> 15:55.710
HOW LONG WOULD IT TAKE
TO GET THE RIMS OFF A CAR?

15:55.750 --> 15:57.047
HOW SHOULD I KNOW?

15:57.090 --> 15:59.115
I MEAN, DID THEY BRING
THEIR OWN JACK, OR...

15:59.150 --> 16:01.618
LOOK, I ALREADY TOLD
ALL THIS STUFF TO THE COPS.

16:01.660 --> 16:04.288
WHY DO I NEED TO SAY IT AGAIN
TO YOU?

16:04.330 --> 16:06.719
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

16:09.900 --> 16:11.993
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

16:23.180 --> 16:24.704
YOU GONNA LET ME IN?

16:24.750 --> 16:27.742
WELL, I'M TRYING TO ACT
LIKE I DON'T KNOW YOU, BUT...

16:30.090 --> 16:32.149
I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DO IT.

16:34.320 --> 16:38.882
IT'S MORE OF AN INNATE ABILITY
TO COMPARTMENTALIZE.

16:38.930 --> 16:42.798
LOOK, I FEEL LIKE I'M WAITING
FOR A TIP OR SOMETHING.

16:42.830 --> 16:45.025
CAN YOU LET ME IN?

16:49.070 --> 16:51.265
MY FIRST GIRLFRIEND
WAS MURDERED.

16:51.310 --> 16:54.768
MY LAST GIRLFRIEND
NEARLY GOT SHOTGUNNED

16:54.810 --> 16:56.607
BY A P.C.H.er DRIVE-BY.

16:56.640 --> 17:00.440
COLOR ME CRAZY,
BUT I SEE A PATTERN.

17:02.250 --> 17:04.582
I'M TRYING TO PROTECT YOU.

17:17.970 --> 17:20.188
SO WHEN DID YOUR FOLKS
SPLIT UP?

17:20.240 --> 17:25.303
MM, JUST A YEAR AGO.

17:26.640 --> 17:28.801
THEY TELL YOU WHY?

17:28.840 --> 17:32.207
THE OFFICIAL ANSWER --
THEY GREW APART.

17:32.250 --> 17:33.808
UNOFFICIALLY,

17:33.850 --> 17:37.616
I KEPT HEARING THEM SCREAM
AT EACH OTHER ABOUT MONEY.

17:37.650 --> 17:39.049
HANNAH?

17:39.090 --> 17:43.322
HI, DAD.
THIS IS LOGAN.

17:44.460 --> 17:46.052
HELLO.

17:49.660 --> 17:53.232
AND THERE'S
THE GRIFFITH CHARM.

17:53.270 --> 17:57.502
SORRY. THAT'S ABOUT THE MOST
YOU'LL GET OUT OF DAD.

18:02.040 --> 18:04.349
[ TOILET FLUSHES ]

18:05.410 --> 18:08.243
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
WITH MY DAUGHTER?

18:08.280 --> 18:10.487
YOU WANT THE COMPLETE
PLAY-BY-PLAY?

18:10.520 --> 18:11.919
THAT'S KIND OF TWISTED.

18:11.950 --> 18:13.417
I WANT YOU
TO GET OUT OF MY HOUSE

18:13.460 --> 18:14.654
AND NEVER SPEAK
TO HER AGAIN.

18:14.690 --> 18:16.351
YOU REALLY WANT THAT
TO HAPPEN?

18:16.390 --> 18:18.585
YOU BETTER RETHINK
WHAT YOU SAW ON THE BRIDGE.

18:18.630 --> 18:21.190
SCRATCH THAT. WHAT THE
FITZPATRICKS TOLD YOU YOU SAW.

18:21.230 --> 18:24.859
YOU CAN'T THREATEN ME,
YOU LITTLE PUNK.
I WOULDN'T BE HERE
IF YOU COULDN'T BE THREATENED.

18:24.900 --> 18:27.733
YOU WANT TO EXPLAIN TO HANNAH
WHY YOU'RE REALLY HERE,

18:27.770 --> 18:28.964
TRY AND BULLY ME?

18:29.000 --> 18:30.729
WELL, WHY DON'T YOU
TELL HER?

18:30.770 --> 18:33.671
SOUNDS LIKE YOU GUYS
ARE ALREADY SO CLOSE.

18:33.710 --> 18:36.270
I'M SURE
SHE'LL SEE THINGS YOUR WAY.

18:36.310 --> 18:37.868
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.

18:37.910 --> 18:39.241
WHILE YOU'RE AT IT,

18:39.280 --> 18:41.009
TRY EXPLAINING
WHY YOU NEVER MENTIONED

18:41.050 --> 18:44.019
HOW YOU'RE THE MYSTERY WITNESS
IN MY MURDER CASE.

18:44.050 --> 18:45.586
THAT'LL BE GOOD.

18:45.620 --> 18:46.541
HMM.

18:46.590 --> 18:48.148
I GUESS
THAT NEVER CAME UP

18:48.190 --> 18:50.488
ON YOUR DRIVE HOME
FROM THE CARNIVAL.

18:50.530 --> 18:53.590
I'M THINKING
WE'RE DONE HERE.

18:53.630 --> 18:56.326
I DON'T WANT TO KEEP
HANNAH WAITING.

19:02.040 --> 19:03.337
YOU'RE JOKING.

19:03.370 --> 19:05.304
TERRENCE COOK WANTS
ANOTHER FAVOR.

19:05.340 --> 19:08.503
FRANKLY, I'M NOT SURE HE WANTS
TO OWE ME ANY MORE

19:08.540 --> 19:10.007
THAN HE ALREADY DOES.

19:10.040 --> 19:12.873
WELL, HE THINKS YOU MIGHT HAVE
SECURITY FOOTAGE OF HIM

19:12.910 --> 19:18.246
FROM SEPTEMBER 13 OF LAST YEAR,
THE DAY OF THE BUS CRASH.

19:20.760 --> 19:22.910
AND WHAT'S HE PAYING YOU,
MR. MARS?

19:22.960 --> 19:25.326
$400 A DAY.

19:25.360 --> 19:28.454
THAT'S $400 A DAY
HE SHOULD BE PAYING ME.

19:28.500 --> 19:31.560
TERRENCE COOK'S GONNA GET
CHARGED WITH MURDER ANY DAY NOW.

19:31.600 --> 19:34.330
TERRENCE COOK OWES ME
A SIGNIFICANT AMOUNT OF MONEY.

19:34.370 --> 19:36.838
THAT'S WHERE MY INTEREST IN HIM
BEGINS AND ENDS.

19:36.870 --> 19:39.509
THEY CAN SWING HIM
FROM THE RAl-TERS FOR ALL I CARE.

19:39.540 --> 19:40.837
MAYBE ALL THAT SWINGING

19:40.880 --> 19:43.576
WILL DROP SOME CHANGE
FROM HIS POCKETS.

19:43.610 --> 19:47.216
IT MIGHT BE A LITTLE HARD TO GET
PAID BY AN INCARCERATED MAN.

19:49.550 --> 19:52.519
REGGIE...
CHECK THE TAPES.

19:52.550 --> 19:54.609
SEE WHAT YOU COME UP WITH.

19:55.320 --> 19:57.880
DO YOU LIKE TO GAMBLE,
MR. MARS?

19:57.930 --> 20:00.956
PERHAPS I COULD INTEREST YOU
IN A LINE OF CREDIT.

20:01.000 --> 20:02.422
NO, THAN KS.

20:03.770 --> 20:04.862
GOOD MAN.

20:04.900 --> 20:08.165
HERE'S A COUPLE OF BUCKS
ON THE HOUSE, THEN.

20:08.200 --> 20:10.668
HAVE SOME FUN
WHILE YOU'RE WAITING.

20:19.210 --> 20:20.677
SEE?

20:20.720 --> 20:24.611
WASN'T THIS BETTER
THAN CHAMPAGNE AND OCEAN VIEWS?

20:28.960 --> 20:31.326
UNTIL TOMORROW.

20:34.260 --> 20:36.956
[ DOOR CLOSES,
ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

20:44.170 --> 20:47.333
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU,
HANNAH.

21:08.160 --> 21:10.560
IT'S TWO BUCKS, BUDDY.

21:14.400 --> 21:17.335
Dealer:
AND KING MAKES 22.

21:21.140 --> 21:23.745
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

21:23.780 --> 21:25.975
OH, MAN, CHO'S
IS GOING OFF TONIGHT.

21:26.010 --> 21:27.443
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENS

21:27.480 --> 21:29.175
WHEN THE CHAINS STOP
DELIVERING TO SOUTH NEPTUNE.

21:29.220 --> 21:31.586
CHO'S 'ZA.
YEAH. NO PROBLEMO.

21:31.620 --> 21:34.453
CAN I GET YOUR NAME
AND NUMBER, PLEASE?

21:35.990 --> 21:38.322
MM-HMM.

21:41.730 --> 21:45.359
JORGE ZIDEO IS A RINGER.
HIS NAME'S ON CARMEN'S LIST.

21:45.400 --> 21:47.391
SO ARE YOU READY
TO BE THE BAIT, CORNY?

21:47.440 --> 21:48.998
HELL, YEAH.
NO ONE'S BETTER.

21:49.040 --> 21:52.066
I'M WHAT YOU'D CALL
THE "MASTER BAIT."

21:52.110 --> 21:54.806
[ BELL CHIMES ]

21:57.240 --> 22:01.609
THERE YOU GO. STRAIGHT OFF
THE SURVEILLANCE HARD DRIVE.

22:05.790 --> 22:08.008
THERE'S FIVE MINUTES
MISSING.

22:08.060 --> 22:10.722
MAYBE HE WAS IN THE JOHN
OR THE ELEVATOR.

22:10.760 --> 22:11.954
I DON'T KNOW.

22:11.990 --> 22:15.050
THAT TERRENCE COOK
IS A MIGHTY SLIPPERY FELLOW.

22:16.060 --> 22:18.392
I NEED A PICTURE OF HIM
AT EXACTLY 7:03.

22:18.430 --> 22:20.489
THESE AREN'T GOING TO HELP.

22:37.650 --> 22:40.915
YOU GOT TO TAKE IT OUTSIDE.

22:40.960 --> 22:42.188
YOUR CELLPHONE.

22:42.220 --> 22:44.825
WE JAM ALL THE SIGNALS
IN A 100-YARD RADIUS.

22:44.860 --> 22:46.680
CARD CHEATERS.
YOU KNOW.

22:48.160 --> 22:49.252
THAN KS.

22:49.300 --> 22:50.426
SURE.

22:50.470 --> 22:52.688
ALL RIGHT.
HAVE A GOOD ONE.

23:13.150 --> 23:15.618
[ GRUNTS ]

23:15.660 --> 23:18.754
[ GROWLS, BARKS ]

23:18.790 --> 23:21.054
TELL -- TELL HIM TO CHILL.

23:22.260 --> 23:23.693
DOWN, BOY.

23:23.730 --> 23:25.595
WHAT'S YOUR NAME, KID?

23:26.530 --> 23:27.861
DO YOU WANT TO DEAL
WITH ME,

23:27.900 --> 23:30.539
OR DO YOU WANT TO DEAL
WITH MR. CHOMPERS?

23:31.110 --> 23:32.566
ARTURO.

23:32.610 --> 23:34.874
WHO ARE YOU WORKING WITH,
ARTURO?

23:34.910 --> 23:36.730
I'M NOT WORKING
WITH NO ONE.

23:36.780 --> 23:39.874
YOU'RE TELLING ME YOU TOOK DOWN
A VARSITY JOCK, JACKED HIS CAR,

23:39.910 --> 23:42.344
STOLE HIS RIMS
ALL BY YOUR SCRAWNY SELF?

23:42.380 --> 23:43.938
NO.
THAT WASN'T ME.

23:43.990 --> 23:45.844
THE OTHERS WAS.
NO, I HEARD ABOUT.

23:45.890 --> 23:48.188
I FIGURED I HAD ME
MY OWN COPYCAT.

23:48.220 --> 23:49.710
COOL, HUH?

23:49.760 --> 23:51.819
GIVE ME A BREAK, MAN.
YOU'RE SOME PUNK FRESHMAN.

23:51.860 --> 23:54.624
NOW GIVE ME BACK MY TUNES
BEFORE I KICK YOUR ASS.

23:54.660 --> 23:56.389
JUST WAIT TILL I'M A P.C.H.er,
SHAGGY.

23:56.430 --> 23:59.092
THEN I'M GONNA FIND YOUR ASS,
AND YOU'RE GONNA GET YOURS.

23:59.130 --> 24:01.098
THUMPER TELLING YOU
TO ROB PIZZA BOYS?

24:01.140 --> 24:04.439
NO, I'M PROVING MYSELF
SO HE'LL LET ME IN.

24:04.470 --> 24:06.859
P.C.H. IS BACK IN CHARGE,
LADY.

24:07.740 --> 24:10.903
DID YOU
JUST CALL ME "LADY"?

24:10.950 --> 24:12.599
OKAY.

24:12.650 --> 24:14.174
SO THE BLACKMAILING --

24:14.220 --> 24:16.916
IS THAT ANOTHER WAY YOU'RE OUT
PROVING YOURSELF, CHOLITO?

24:16.950 --> 24:20.113
MAN, WHAT ARE YOU TALKING
ABOUT?

24:20.150 --> 24:21.788
BLACK-WHATTING?

24:24.730 --> 24:26.425
THANKS FOR YOUR COOPERATION.

24:26.460 --> 24:28.496
LOOKS LIKE WE'RE DONE HERE,
ARTURO.

24:28.530 --> 24:29.497
COOL.

24:29.530 --> 24:32.522
CAN I GO HOME, THEN?

24:32.570 --> 24:34.595
ALMOST.

25:17.180 --> 25:20.343
I NEED YOU TO GET ME
INTO A RESTRICTED WEBSITE.

25:20.380 --> 25:21.938
SURE, WHAT'S THE ADDRESS?

25:21.980 --> 25:23.049
I DON'T KNOW.

25:23.080 --> 25:24.638
WHAT'S IT FOR?

25:24.690 --> 25:29.184
IT'S A NEPTUNE HIGH
GAY CHAT ROOM.

25:30.260 --> 25:31.818
VERONICA, YOU'RE NOT...

25:31.860 --> 25:34.294
NO, I'M JUST CURIOUS.

25:35.530 --> 25:37.088
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:37.130 --> 25:41.237
CURIOUS AS TO WHAT'S POSTED ON
THE WEBSITE, MORE ACCURATELY.

25:41.270 --> 25:43.807
HERE WE GO.

25:43.840 --> 25:46.536
WORK YOUR FUNKY MAGIC.

25:47.980 --> 25:51.279
AND NOTHING.
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

25:52.950 --> 25:54.611
YOU SET IT UP, DIDN'T YOU?

25:54.650 --> 25:57.915
SOME ASS-FACE GOT ONTO
THEIR MESSAGE BOARD

25:57.950 --> 26:00.248
AND WROTE SOME
PRETTY AWFUL STUFF,

26:00.290 --> 26:02.815
SO RYAN ASKED ME
TO BEEF UP THEIR SECURITY.

26:02.860 --> 26:04.885
YEAH, I WORK FOR RYAN,
TOO, NOW.

26:04.930 --> 26:06.454
SO IF YOU COULD JUST --

26:06.490 --> 26:09.948
SO THEN WHY WOULDN'T
HE HAVE LET YOU ON IT HIMSELF?

26:10.000 --> 26:12.924
DAMN YOU
AND YOUR VALID QUESTIONS.

26:12.970 --> 26:14.369
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:14.400 --> 26:18.131
LOOK, IT'S STILL PRIVATE IF I
ONLY SEE THE USERNAMES, RIGHT?

26:18.170 --> 26:19.933
SAWY DETECT IVES
SUCH AS YOURSELF

26:19.970 --> 26:22.507
MIGHT DEDUCE WHO
THE PIRATE'S S.H.I.P.ers ARE.

26:22.540 --> 26:25.043
[ SIGHS ]

26:25.080 --> 26:28.470
MAC, THE ONLY WAY I CAN STOP
THE MARLENAS AND KYLEES

26:28.520 --> 26:30.909
OF THIS SCHOOL
FROM BEING TORMENTED

26:30.950 --> 26:33.384
IS IF I GET ON
THAT MESSAGE BOARD.

26:33.420 --> 26:37.049
ALL RIGHT, STOP IT.
YOU'RE EMBARRASSING ME.

26:37.090 --> 26:38.648
[ SIGHS ]

26:38.690 --> 26:40.624
[ SIGHS ]

26:49.540 --> 26:52.361
OKAY, I'LL MAKE YOU
A HARD COPY,

26:52.410 --> 26:55.277
BUT YOU HAVE TO BURN IT
WHEN YOU'RE DONE.

27:12.030 --> 27:13.327
Veronica: EXCUSE ME, COACH?

27:13.360 --> 27:14.850
THINK I COULD RIDE
WITH THE TEAM TONIGHT?

27:14.900 --> 27:16.356
MY CAR'S IN THE SHOP,

27:16.400 --> 27:18.459
AND I PROMISED YOUR
STAR POINT GUARD I'D BE THERE.

27:19.100 --> 27:21.660
DID I MENTION
ALL THE ACTION SHOTS I'LL TAKE

27:21.700 --> 27:22.962
FOR THE NAVIGATOR?

27:23.000 --> 27:24.558
I'M SORRY, VERONICA,

27:24.610 --> 27:27.738
WE HAVE A STRICT RULE
AGAINST GIRLS ON THE TEAM BUS.

27:27.780 --> 27:29.099
I WANT THEM FOCUSED.

27:29.140 --> 27:32.200
YOU CAN RIDE
WITH ME IF YOU WANT.

27:33.410 --> 27:36.811
I REALIZE IT'S NO BUS FILLED
WITH ROWDY TOWEL-SNAPPING JOCKS,

27:36.850 --> 27:38.317
BUT IT'LL SMELL BETTER.

27:38.350 --> 27:40.113
I DON'T KNOW.
UM...

27:40.150 --> 27:43.381
DO YOU HAVE ROOM
FOR MY GIANT FOAM FINGER?

27:43.420 --> 27:45.524
I DO, AND I CAN EVEN
DROP YOU OFF AROUND THE BLOCK

27:45.560 --> 27:48.290
IF YOU'RE WORRIED
ABOUT BEING SEEN TOGETHER.

27:49.530 --> 27:50.861
YES.

27:50.900 --> 27:55.769
PLEASE, BY ALL MEANS,
PROTECT MY REPUTATION.

28:07.980 --> 28:11.347
DON'T BLAME MAC.
I MADE HER PRINT IT OUT.

28:11.390 --> 28:13.244
I DON'T CARE WHO'S GAY.

28:13.290 --> 28:14.518
THAT'S FINE.

28:14.560 --> 28:16.289
I JUST DIDN'T WANT TO LET YOU
ONTO THE SITE MYSELF.

28:16.320 --> 28:18.129
I'VE LET THOSE GUYS DOWN
ENOUGH.

28:18.160 --> 28:19.957
RYAN,
WE CAUGHT THE MUGGER.

28:19.990 --> 28:22.458
HE DOESN'T HAVE THE CRANIAL
RESOURCES TO SPELL BLACKMAIL,

28:22.500 --> 28:24.297
LET ALONE PERFORM IT.

28:24.330 --> 28:27.629
THE LIST GETTING OUT
ISN'T YOUR FAULT.

28:27.670 --> 28:29.160
IT NEVER WAS.

28:29.200 --> 28:31.430
I THINK THE BLACKMAILER
IS ONE OF YOUR OWN POSTERS.

28:31.470 --> 28:32.300
WHAT?

28:32.340 --> 28:34.171
YOU'RE SERIOUS?

28:34.210 --> 28:36.235
I WAS LOOKING THROUGH
SOME OLD CHATS.

28:36.280 --> 28:37.599
UM, HERE.

28:37.640 --> 28:40.609
BACK IN JULY, THIS GUY
WHO CALLS HIMSELF "MIZZ P."

28:40.650 --> 28:44.643
WENT OFF ABOUT "THE OUTING
OF ALL OUTINGS IN NEPTUNE,"

28:44.690 --> 28:45.884
AND THEN HE VANISHED.

28:45.920 --> 28:47.683
A TAD OMINOUS,
DON'T YOU THINK?

28:47.720 --> 28:51.326
MIZZ P. AIN'T THE BAD GUY,
VERONICA.

28:51.360 --> 28:54.693
HIS NAME WAS PETER FERRAIRE,
AND...

28:54.730 --> 28:56.527
HE DIED IN THE BUS CRASH.

28:56.560 --> 28:57.925
OH, I'M --

28:57.970 --> 28:59.767
AND THERE'S BEEN
ANOTHER BLACKMAILING LETTER.

28:59.800 --> 29:01.233
WHO ARE THEY Al-TER NOW?

29:02.070 --> 29:03.492
OH, YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS?

29:03.540 --> 29:05.929
I TOLD THE VICTIM THEY COULD
COME TO YOU FOR HELP, BUT...

29:05.970 --> 29:08.109
I WOULDN'T HOLD YOUR BREATH
ON THIS ONE.

29:08.140 --> 29:09.437
GREAT.

29:09.480 --> 29:12.347
I'LL JUST HEAD OUT INTO THE HALL
AND LOOK FOR THE GUY

29:12.380 --> 29:15.838
IN THE BLACK HAT
TWIRLING HIS MOUSTACHE.

29:32.970 --> 29:34.938
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

29:34.970 --> 29:36.130
THAT DEPENDS.

29:36.170 --> 29:38.229
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA
LET ME DO?

29:38.270 --> 29:39.464
LOOK...

29:39.510 --> 29:41.774
I KNOW YOU STABBED
THAT KID ON THE BRIDGE.

29:41.810 --> 29:43.038
MY DAD TOLD ME EVERYTHING.

29:43.080 --> 29:44.968
NO, YOUR DAD IS A LIAR.

29:45.010 --> 29:48.138
I DIDN'T KILL ANYONE, HANNAH.
YOUR DAD WASN'T EVEN THERE.

29:48.180 --> 29:49.909
I WAS WORRIED YOU WERE
EMBARRASSED OF ME,

29:49.950 --> 29:51.713
AND YOU WERE JUST USING ME.

29:51.750 --> 29:53.115
WHEN I MET YOU
AT THE CARNIVAL,

29:53.150 --> 29:54.981
I HAD NO IDEA
WHO YOU WERE, I SWEAR.

29:55.020 --> 29:56.385
LOOK, THE REASON YOUR PARENTS

29:56.420 --> 29:58.479
WERE FIGHTING
ABOUT MONEY ALL THE TIME --

29:58.530 --> 30:00.680
IT'S BECAUSE YOUR DAD
WAS BLOWING IT ON COKE.

30:00.730 --> 30:03.790
MY DAD'S A COKEHEAD?
PLEASE, HE'S A DOCTOR, LOGAN.

30:03.830 --> 30:05.263
AND THAT'S WHY
A JURY'S GONNA BUY IT

30:05.300 --> 30:07.359
WHEN HE TELLS THEM
I KILLED FELIX.

30:08.540 --> 30:11.134
YOUR DAD IS IN DEEP
TO THE FITZPATRICK FAMILY,

30:11.170 --> 30:14.401
THE ONES WHO REALLY WANTED
FELIX DEAD.

30:17.280 --> 30:19.874
AND I'M SUPPOSED
TO BELIEVE YOU.

30:19.910 --> 30:21.673
YOU DO BELIEVE ME.

30:22.650 --> 30:25.813
WHAT I'M SAYING MAKES
A LOT OF SENSE, DOESN'T IT?

30:31.230 --> 30:34.859
LET ME GO, LOGAN.
PLEASE?

30:36.660 --> 30:38.867
YEAH.

30:38.900 --> 30:40.891
JUST THINK ABOUT IT.

30:41.940 --> 30:44.431
CHECK AROUND THE HOUSE.
KEEP AN OPEN MIND.

30:46.410 --> 30:48.674
I FOUND OUR SILVER BULLET,
TERRENCE.

30:48.710 --> 30:52.498
YOU COULDN'T HAVE MADE THE CALL
THAT BLEW UP THE BUS.

30:52.550 --> 30:54.916
SURVEILLANCE SHOTS.

30:54.950 --> 30:56.440
TA- DA!

30:56.480 --> 31:00.587
NO CELL SIGNAL ANYWHERE
IN THE SEVEN RIVERS CASINO.

31:01.620 --> 31:03.952
WHAT YOU GOT IS PROOF
THAT I WAS IN A PRIVATE MEETING

31:03.990 --> 31:05.548
WITH LEONARD LOBO.

31:06.790 --> 31:10.556
YOU WERE IN A LEGAL GAMBLING
VENUE PLACING LEGAL BETS.

31:10.600 --> 31:13.194
LOBO'S NAME IS ON THE LEAGUE
UNSAVORY-CHARACTERS LIST.

31:13.230 --> 31:15.630
HE WAS SUSPECTED OF,
BUT NEVER CONVICTED OF,

31:15.670 --> 31:18.059
FIXING A COLLEGE BASKETBALL GAME
BACK IN THE '805.

31:18.110 --> 31:21.500
IF I ADMIT
THAT I WAS IN HIS OFFICE,

31:21.540 --> 31:23.508
I MAKE MYSELF
THE NEXT PETE ROSE.

31:23.540 --> 31:26.179
WE'LL TAKE THESE PHOTOS
TO THE SHERIFF,

31:26.210 --> 31:28.178
AND I'LL MAKE SURE
THEY DON'T GET OUT.

31:28.220 --> 31:30.575
ALL YOU NEED
IS A LITTLE LEVERAGE.

31:49.170 --> 31:50.637
Veronica: "KUZZIKAN"?

31:50.670 --> 31:53.901
IT'S MY BROTHER'S CAR.
BROTHER'S PLATES.

31:53.940 --> 31:58.877
WHEREAS YOUR PERSONALIZED PLATES
MIGHT READ...

31:58.910 --> 32:01.117
"KISSNKUZN."

32:02.320 --> 32:04.686
YOU DIDN'T GET MUGGED,
DID YOU?

32:07.290 --> 32:08.518
NO.

32:08.560 --> 32:12.929
YOU NEEDED TO MAKE SOME FAST
CASH, ISN'T THAT RIGHT?

32:14.730 --> 32:16.288
YES.

32:17.060 --> 32:18.561
YOU'RE GAY, AREN'T YOU?

32:25.970 --> 32:27.403
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

32:27.440 --> 32:29.601
I WANT TO KNOW
WHY YOU ACT LIKE YOU DO.

32:29.640 --> 32:33.474
THE OTHER DAY WHEN YOU AND YOUR
PAL WERE MAKING FUN OF DICK.

32:33.510 --> 32:37.173
WHEN UNDERNEATH I WAS REALLY
JUST BASHING MYSELF.

32:37.220 --> 32:40.041
VERY INSIGHTFUL.
WANT TO KNOW WHY I DO IT?

32:40.090 --> 32:43.753
BECAUSE I WANT TO SURVIVE
HIGH SCHOOL, OKAY?

32:43.790 --> 32:47.556
SO YOU HOCK YOUR OWN RIMS
FOR CASH TO PAY THE BLACKMAILER,

32:47.590 --> 32:50.150
USE THE PIZZA-BOY MUGGINGS
AS A COVER,

32:50.200 --> 32:52.760
THEN BUY NEW RIMS
WITH THE INSURANCE MONEY.

32:52.800 --> 32:54.495
SOUNDS BAD
WHEN YOU SAY IT.

32:54.540 --> 32:55.632
VERONICA...

32:55.670 --> 33:01.131
YOU REALIZE PEOPLE HERE FIND OUT
I'M QUEER...

33:01.180 --> 33:03.034
AND I'M DEAD.

33:03.080 --> 33:04.570
I'M NOT OUT TO OUT YOU.

33:04.610 --> 33:06.999
I JUST WANT TO PAY
THE DAMN MONEY

33:07.050 --> 33:10.213
AND BE DONE
WITH THIS WHOLE NIGHTMARE.

33:12.320 --> 33:14.857
THE NOTE --
LET ME LOOK AT IT.

33:14.890 --> 33:19.554
IT WAS JUST AN E-MAIL FROM
SOME GUY NAMED RICK SANTORUM.

33:19.590 --> 33:22.718
HE SAYS HE WANTS ME
TO JUST MAIL IT TO HIM.

33:22.760 --> 33:25.160
HE GAVE A LOCAL ADDRESS.

33:26.300 --> 33:29.337
HE GAVE YOU AN ADDRESS?

33:32.110 --> 33:34.476
[ BEEPING ]

33:39.710 --> 33:42.110
[ BEEPING ]

34:09.010 --> 34:12.138
RICK SANTORUM'S ADDRESS
IS A FAKE.

34:12.180 --> 34:13.545
NO SURPRISE THERE.

34:13.580 --> 34:15.468
KELLY MAILED
HIS BLACKMAIL PAYOFF,

34:15.520 --> 34:17.579
BUT IT'S BEEN STALLED
AT THE POST OFFICE.

34:17.620 --> 34:19.713
IT'S BEEN LIKE WAITING
FOR A TOASTER TO POP

34:19.750 --> 34:21.183
THESE PAST SEVEN HOURS.

34:21.220 --> 34:22.653
WELL, I'LL WATCH IT
IF YOU DON'T HAVE THE TIME.

34:22.690 --> 34:24.180
I'LL CALL YOU
IF I SEE ANYTHING.

34:24.230 --> 34:26.084
NO NEED.

34:26.130 --> 34:27.529
IT FINALLY MOVED.

34:27.560 --> 34:30.723
LET'S SEE
WHERE THE PACKAGE ENDED UP.

34:30.760 --> 34:32.762
HUBBELL STREET?

34:32.800 --> 34:36.031
I KNOW WHO LIVES THERE.
I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

34:36.070 --> 34:38.231
Veronica:
HEY, BLACKMAILER.

34:38.270 --> 34:42.138
I FIGURED I'D BE SEEING YOU
SOMETIME TODAY.

34:42.180 --> 34:43.807
LOOKING FOR THIS?

34:43.840 --> 34:46.638
MOST PEOPLE JUST GET PISSED AND
SMASH IT INTO A MILLION PIECES,

34:46.680 --> 34:48.671
BUT THEY'RE KIND OF EXPENSIVE,
SO THANKS.

34:48.720 --> 34:51.109
[ Laughing ] AND I THOUGHT
I WAS BEING SO CLEVER

34:51.150 --> 34:53.311
WITH THE WHOLE
DEAD-LETTER-OFFICE THING.

34:53.350 --> 34:54.886
PRETTY CLEVER.

34:54.920 --> 34:56.751
YOU KNEW THE MONEY WOULD MAKE
ITS WAY TO THE POST OFFICE.

34:56.790 --> 34:59.156
HOW'D YOU EVER GET IN
TO RETRIEVE THE PACKAGE?

34:59.190 --> 35:00.623
MY MOM WORKS THERE.

35:00.660 --> 35:02.355
OOH, NICE.

35:03.300 --> 35:06.098
SO I'M ASSUMING
KELLY WANTS HIS MONEY BACK.

35:06.130 --> 35:07.825
SAFE ASSUMPTION.

35:07.870 --> 35:09.360
WHY'D YOU DO IT?

35:09.400 --> 35:11.868
I WANTED TO GET OUT OF NEPTUNE
AI-TER GRADUATION.

35:11.910 --> 35:13.036
THERE GOES THAT PLAN.

35:13.070 --> 35:14.674
COMMUNITY COLLEGE,
HERE I COME.

35:14.710 --> 35:18.100
BESIDES, I DIDN'T CARE MUCH
ABOUT SELF-HATING "KISSNKUZN."

35:18.150 --> 35:19.947
I WOULD HAVE SLEPT
JUST FINE

35:19.980 --> 35:22.278
KNOWING THAT KELLY KUZZIO
WAS DRIVING AROUND RIMLESS.

35:22.320 --> 35:25.141
WHY'D YOU OUT MARLENA?

35:25.190 --> 35:27.340
'CAUSE I'M A HORRIBLE,
CRAZY BITCH.

35:27.390 --> 35:29.187
YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHAT'S WORSE?

35:29.220 --> 35:31.450
I TOLD HER THE BLACKMAILER
WAS BLUFFING.

35:31.490 --> 35:33.879
I TOLD HER NOT TO PAY.

35:33.930 --> 35:35.693
I DON'T GET IT.

35:35.730 --> 35:38.290
I WANTED TO BE OUT, BUT I WANTED
MARLENA OUT WITH ME.

35:38.330 --> 35:41.163
I WANTED TO BE ABLE
TO WALK DOWN THE HALLS WITH HER,

35:41.200 --> 35:42.497
LIKE A REAL COUPLE.

35:42.540 --> 35:46.260
SO SHE DIDN'T WANT TO COME OUT,
AND YOU DID?

35:46.310 --> 35:47.902
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

35:47.940 --> 35:51.171
I WANT TO TELL MARLENA MYSELF,
IF THAT'S OKAY.

35:51.210 --> 35:52.905
OKAY.

35:57.720 --> 36:01.315
[ STARSAILOR'S
"I DON'T KNOW'' PLAYS ]

36:08.630 --> 36:11.861
* WOKE UP REELING

36:11.900 --> 36:14.596
* LOST ALL FEELING

36:14.640 --> 36:17.200
* HEART ON THE FLOOR

36:17.240 --> 36:21.028
YOU WERE RIGHT
ABOUT MY DAD.

36:21.070 --> 36:23.732
* TRIED TO STOP ME

36:23.780 --> 36:28.342
* BUT I WAS NOT LISTENING

36:28.380 --> 36:31.440
* ONE MORE DRINK AND

36:31.490 --> 36:34.084
* I WON'T MISS THEM

36:34.120 --> 36:37.157
* I DON'T KNOW WHAT LOVE IS

36:37.190 --> 36:40.387
* I DON'T KNOW WHAT LOVE IS

36:40.430 --> 36:41.954
WHO'S THAT?

36:42.000 --> 36:43.752
HANNAH SOMETHING,
I THINK.

36:43.800 --> 36:46.621
I'D BE A WILLOWY BLONDE, TOO,
IF M DAD WAS A PLASTIC SURGEON.

36:46.670 --> 36:48.069
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:48.100 --> 36:50.739
* SEE THAT POOR GIRL

36:50.770 --> 36:53.307
* WITH THE GLINT IN HER EYE

36:54.010 --> 36:55.409
Veronica: WAIT A MINUTE.

36:55.440 --> 36:57.772
THIS ISN'T THE WAY
TO THE REGIONAL FINALS.

36:57.810 --> 36:59.971
IF MY DAD EXPECTS ME
TO DRIVE 75 MILES

37:00.010 --> 37:03.810
IN THIS BOUNCY, OLD BRONCO,
THEN HE REALLY IS A MURDERER.

37:06.690 --> 37:09.386
OKAY, WHICH ONE IS MONDAY?

37:09.420 --> 37:11.354
YOU LAUGH, BUT HE PRETTY MUCH
USED TO HAVE ONE

37:11.390 --> 37:12.550
FOR EVERY DAY OF THE MONTH.

37:12.590 --> 37:15.525
OUR LIVES ARE SO SIMILAR.

37:15.560 --> 37:18.563
THE MARS FAMILY HANGAR
IS A SPITTING IMAGE OF THIS ONE.

37:18.600 --> 37:20.124
FLYING'S NOT HIS THING.

37:20.170 --> 37:23.492
WOODY GOODMAN LETS DAD USE
THE HANGAR FOR HIS TOYS.

37:25.710 --> 37:27.530
SO...

37:27.570 --> 37:29.401
WHAT ARE YOU
IN THE MOOD FOR?

37:29.440 --> 37:32.876
HOT-BLOODED ITALIAN
OR COOL AND TEUTONIC?

37:32.910 --> 37:34.446
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

37:34.480 --> 37:37.040
HOW ABOUT PRIVILEGED

37:37.080 --> 37:38.889
AND UPPER-CRUSTY?

37:38.920 --> 37:41.286
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:44.790 --> 37:46.121
[ SIGHS ]

37:46.160 --> 37:48.628
I WANT YOU TO ANNOUNCE THAT
TERRENCE COOK HAS BEEN CLEARED

37:48.660 --> 37:50.150
OF SUSPICION
IN THE BUS CRASH.

37:50.200 --> 37:51.360
[ SCOFFS ] WHAT?

37:52.000 --> 37:54.468
THIS SOME KIND
OF JEDI MIND TRICK?

37:54.500 --> 37:56.536
WHY WOULD I WANT TO DO THAT?

38:01.880 --> 38:03.905
EXACTLY WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO BE LOOKING AT?

38:03.940 --> 38:05.248
HIS ALIBI.

38:05.280 --> 38:06.577
[ LAUGHS ]

38:06.610 --> 38:08.441
YOU CAUGHT TERRENCE
AT A CASINO, HUH?

38:08.480 --> 38:10.038
THERE'S A SURPRISE.

38:10.080 --> 38:13.311
THOSE TIME STAMPS SAY THAT HE
WAS AT THE SEVEN RIVERS CASINO

38:13.350 --> 38:15.011
AT THE TIME
OF THE EXPLOSION.

38:15.060 --> 38:17.119
AT 7:01 AND 7:06.

38:17.160 --> 38:20.254
COULD HAVE BEEN OFF
AND MADE A CALL BETWEEN THEN.

38:20.290 --> 38:22.190
THE CASINO BLOCKS CELL
RECEPTION.

38:22.230 --> 38:23.857
PAY PHONES.

38:23.900 --> 38:25.925
YOU REALLY THINK SOMEONE WOULD
MAKE A PHONE CALL ON A LAND LINE

38:25.970 --> 38:28.359
THAT WOULD KILL A BUS FULL
OF PEOPLE FROM A LOCATION

38:28.400 --> 38:32.063
THAT HAS 4,000 CAMERAS
AND 300 SECURITY PERSONNEL?

38:32.110 --> 38:35.876
SUBPOENA THE PHONE RECORDS,
CHECK THE CALLS.

38:35.910 --> 38:38.208
UGH, SOUNDS LIKE
A LOT OF WORK.

38:38.240 --> 38:40.208
WHAT'S YOUR BEEF WITH ME,
SHERIFF?

38:40.250 --> 38:42.468
MY BEEF?

38:42.520 --> 38:45.717
I SUPPOSE IT'S THAT YOU KILLED
A BUSLOAD OF KIDS

38:45.750 --> 38:47.411
JUST TO TIDY UP
YOUR LOVE LIFE.

38:47.450 --> 38:50.749
CRAZY GIRLFRIEND WHO KNEW ABOUT
YOU BETTING ON BASEBALL --

38:50.790 --> 38:53.122
THAT'S A LIABILITY
YOU COULD NOT AFFORD.

38:57.030 --> 38:59.567
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
PRESS CHARGES, LAMB.

38:59.600 --> 39:02.296
WHATEVER YOU SAY, BOSS.

39:04.670 --> 39:06.365
[ GASPS ] WHAT'S THIS?

39:06.410 --> 39:08.571
PLAY IT.

39:10.510 --> 39:13.570
I REALLY HOPE
THIS IS THE NEW BIG & RICH.

39:20.950 --> 39:23.589
Lamb: I GOT A GUY
IN A HOLDING CELL BACK THERE,

39:23.620 --> 39:25.156
SAYS YOU DID FAVORS

39:25.190 --> 39:29.194
FOR GENTLEMEN WHO BET
EXT ENSIVELY ON BASEBALL,

39:29.230 --> 39:30.925
AND HE WANTS TO MAKE A DEAL.

39:30.960 --> 39:33.793
ME, I WOULD MUCH RATHER DEAL
WITH YOU.

39:33.830 --> 39:35.730
ALL RIGHT,
WHERE'D YOU GET IT?

39:35.770 --> 39:37.692
I DON'T THINK
A GRAND JURY WILL HAVE
A HARD TIME FIGURING IT OUT.

39:37.740 --> 39:39.833
YOU DON'T BACK OFF,
SHERIFF,

39:39.870 --> 39:42.998
AND THAT RECORDING IS GOING
STRAIGHT TO WOODY GOODMAN,

39:43.040 --> 39:46.908
NEWSPAPERS, YOUR GRANDMAMA.

39:46.950 --> 39:48.042
RIGHT.

39:48.080 --> 39:50.878
HERE'S HOW IT'S GONNA PLAY OUT,
SLUGGER.

39:50.920 --> 39:54.879
RELEASE THE TAPE, I LOSE MY $50K
CIVIL-SERVANT JOB.

39:54.920 --> 39:58.083
YOU -- YOU LOSE
YOUR HALL OF FAME INDUCTION,

39:58.120 --> 40:03.353
YOUR COLOR-COMMENTATING GIG,
YOUR ENDORSEMENTS.

40:03.400 --> 40:06.028
WHERE'S THE TRADE IN THAT,
TERRENCE?

40:06.070 --> 40:08.026
Veronica:
THE BOY CAN PLAY BALL.

40:08.070 --> 40:09.935
Jackie: DID YOU SEE HIS
"RUNNING TEARDROP" IN THE LANE?

40:09.970 --> 40:12.700
OH, I SAW IT.
IT WAS JORDAN-ESQUE.

40:12.740 --> 40:18.007
BUT TOMORROW, WE BOTH GOT TO
PROMISE, SAY NOTHING TO HIM.

40:18.040 --> 40:20.099
WE CANNOT FEED THAT EGO.

40:20.150 --> 40:22.243
I LIKE MY WALLACE HUMBLE.

40:22.280 --> 40:25.078
MY DAD TOLD ME THAT YOU'RE
HELPING OUT WITH HIS CASE.

40:25.120 --> 40:27.179
THAT MEANS A LOT,

40:27.220 --> 40:28.858
ESPECIALLY SINCE HE'S ALREADY
BEEN CONVICTED

40:28.890 --> 40:30.812
BY HALF THE PEOPLE
IN NEPTUNE.

40:30.860 --> 40:34.796
WELL, LUCKILY, IT'S THE HALF
I DON'T LIKE, SO IT WORKS OUT.

40:45.210 --> 40:47.166
[ MECHANICAL WHIRRING ]

40:47.210 --> 40:49.303
THIS IS NOT GOOD.

40:49.340 --> 40:51.001
THE TOP'S BROKEN.

40:51.040 --> 40:53.179
IT'S PROBABLY
JUST A BLOWN FUSE.

40:53.210 --> 40:56.816
OKAY, AND YOU SOUND LIKE
YOU KNOW HOW TO FIX IT.

40:56.850 --> 41:00.946
WELL, IF SHE'S ANYTHING LIKE
MY LeBARON UNDER THE BONNET,

41:00.990 --> 41:03.288
I'M GONNA NEED
A PHILLIPS HEAD.

41:03.320 --> 41:05.049
[ Laughing ]
SCREWDRIVER.

41:05.090 --> 41:07.479
[ LAUGHS ]

41:21.440 --> 41:22.873
YOU FIND IT?

41:26.310 --> 41:27.846
Veronica: DAD?

41:27.880 --> 41:30.542
HONEY, WHAT IS IT?
WHAT'S WRONG?

41:33.150 --> 41:35.414
JACKIE AND I BORROWED ONE
OF TERRENCE'S CARS TONIGHT.

41:35.460 --> 41:39.055
I WAS DIGGING AROUND IN
THE HANGAR WHERE HE KEEPS THEM,

41:39.090 --> 41:41.456
AND I FOUND...

41:41.490 --> 41:44.197
I DON'T KNOW.

41:45.230 --> 41:46.697
BUT I'M PRETTY SURE

41:46.730 --> 41:50.166
IT WAS SOME SORT OF EXPLOSIVE
AND DETONATORS.

41:52.840 --> 41:54.808
SO MUCH FOR MY GUT.
